NAME
    App::PlatformInfo - Packed platform-info script

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of App::PlatformInfo (from Perl
    distribution App-PlatformInfo), released on 2019-04-30.

DESCRIPTION
    This distribution provides a "platform-info" which is packed with its
    dependencies so it can run with just perl and core modules.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-PlatformInfo>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-PlatformInfo>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=App-PlatformInfo>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

